<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4949584>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 10. Cnemaspis monachorum (LSUDPC 6502) from the Langkawi Archipelago, Kedah, Peninsular Malaysia. Upper and middle left: ventral color pattern of male (upper; LSUDPC 8275) and female (middle; LSUDPC 8274) from Pulau Langgun. Photographs by ESHQ. Upper right: adult male (LSUDPC 4701) from Wat Wanaram, Pulau Langkawi in the dark color pattern phase. Lower left: adult female (LSUDPC 4846) from Wat Wanaram in the dark color pattern phase. Lower right: karst microhabitat on Pulau Langgun. Photographs by LLG." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4949584/files/figure.png" .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4949582>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
